The paper discusses a software model for probabilistic reasoning and describes how the ICMAUS framework can model various kinds of PR. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computational linguistics (cs.CL), information theory (cs.IT), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
